title: Start
body:
Teenager: Hey there! The zebra crossing is too far from here! Let's just cross the road together! Okay?

		Jenny: But my mom advised me to use zebra-crossing to cross the road.

		Teenager: I will help you to cross the road without zebra crossing.

		Jenny: Should I follow what she said or use zebra crossing instead?

		[[No, it's too dangerous.Let's use the zebra crossing.|ZebraCrossing]]
[[There is less cars on the road, so let's cross.|CrossTheRoad]]

title: ZebraCrossing
body:
Jenny: Yay, I will cross the road safely using zebra crossing.
 Jenny: I should continue my way to grandma house.

title: CrossTheRoad
body: Jenny: Too dangerous! The car nearly hit me!
